  "remarks": "TAi.109 Title: a) Maulavi  b) Mullah. Designation: Governor of Zabol and Uruzgan Provinces under the Taliban regime.  Taliban member responsible for Uruzgan province, Afghanistan, as at early 2007. Brother-in-law of Mullah Mohammed Omar (TI.O.4.01). Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended 21 Sep 2007, 12 Apr. 2010, 29 Nov. 2011, 1 Jun. 2012)",
